{{Location map~ |France Lower Normandy |lat=49.63 |long=-1.62 |label=[[Cherbourg-Octeville|Cherbourg]] |position=top |label_size=80 |marksize=8}}
{{Location map~ |France Lower Normandy |lat=49.2794 |long=-0.7028 |label=[[Bayeux]] |position=bottom |label_size=80 |marksize=8}}
{{Location map~ |France Lower Normandy |lat=49.3 |long=-1.25 |label=[[Carentan]] |position=left |label_size=80 |marksize=8}}
